snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin': Halloween Hack (FNF Mod) (Earthbound: Halloween Hack)
snippet.description:
Play the mod here: https://gamebanana.com/mods/385801

Friday Night Funkin': Halloween Hack was created by me. The mod is about the old hack Toby Fox made before his success with Undertale and Deltarune. It was called "Earthbound: Halloween Hack" This was the first time MEGALOVANIA got introduced to the world. MEGALOVANIA is in this FNF mod as a playable song! Play as Boyfriend and rap battle against Dr. Andonuts to the death!

Friday Night Funkin' is an unfinished rhythm game created by Ninjamuffin and an amazing team of developers such as kawaiisprite and PhantomArcade. FNF is always getting new content and weeks added to it as the years go by. The community is helping the rhythm game rise into popularity with the endless supply of mods that are getting released to the public which end up getting a lot of popularity and views. 

-- Wanna request a song? Email me! --

► Follow my Twitter for updates: https://twitter.com/moikey__

Cya!
